WEBVTT

00:01.160 --> 00:02.661
PREVIOUSLY ON "SALEM"...

00:02.700 --> 00:03.962
John: ISAAC?

00:04.000 --> 00:05.399
Isaac:
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR.

00:05.430 --> 00:07.159
COMING HOME TO SALEM
TO GET OUT OF THE WAR

00:07.200 --> 00:09.737
IS LIKE JUMPING IN THE OCEAN
TO GET OUT OF THE RAIN.

00:09.770 --> 00:11.067
Isaac:
YOU CAN'T LEAVE SALEM JUST YET.

00:11.110 --> 00:12.737
SOMETHING YOU'VE GOT TO SEE.

00:12.780 --> 00:14.532
Mr. Hale:
SOMEONE BROKE OUR CIRCLE.

00:14.580 --> 00:16.172
Mary: WHO SAW US?

00:16.210 --> 00:17.643
Mr. Hale: I DO NOT KNOW.

00:17.680 --> 00:19.238
Mary:
I WAITED FOR YOU.

00:19.280 --> 00:21.248
YEARS AND YEARS.

00:21.280 --> 00:23.817
John: COME WITH ME.

00:23.850 --> 00:26.489
Mary:
I CAN'T. IT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

00:26.520 --> 00:28.056
Tituba:
THE GRAND RITE HAS BEGUN,

00:28.090 --> 00:30.058
AND THE EARTH
CRIES OUT FOR INNOCENT BLOOD.

00:30.090 --> 00:32.149
Mary: I KNOW WELL MY DUTIES.

00:32.200 --> 00:35.089
George: THE ONLY THING
THAT KEEPS ME ALIVE

00:35.130 --> 00:37.269
IS THE LOOK ON YOUR FACE

00:37.300 --> 00:41.566
WHEN JOHN ALDEN
FINDS OUT WHAT YOU REALLY ARE.

00:42.810 --> 00:44.004
Bridget: [ SCREAMING ]

00:44.040 --> 00:45.507
Anne:
FATHER, YOU KNOW BRIDGET.

00:45.540 --> 00:47.337
HOW COULD YOU
THINK HER GUILTY OF THIS?

00:47.380 --> 00:48.779
Mr. Hale: IT ISN'T
A MATTER OF WHAT I THINK.

00:48.810 --> 00:51.108
WHAT A MESS
YOU'VE MADE OF THINGS.

00:51.150 --> 00:52.447
Bridget: [ GASPING ]

00:52.480 --> 00:53.879
Anne: [ SOBBING ]

00:56.990 --> 00:58.082
Mary: I DON'T WANT YOU HERE.

00:58.120 --> 00:59.212
John: I ALMOST BELIEVE YOU.

01:12.270 --> 01:14.158
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

01:33.190 --> 01:36.079
John: YOU'RE SO BEAUTIFUL.

01:41.860 --> 01:44.328
Cotton: "FEAR NO MAN'S WAR,

01:44.370 --> 01:47.669
FOR ONLY A WAR FROM HELL
COULD DESTROY SALEM."

01:47.700 --> 01:50.066
THE DEVIL WAS NEVER GOING TO LET

01:50.110 --> 01:52.670
A PROMISED LAND BE BUILT HERE
WITHOUT A BA'I'I'LE.

01:52.710 --> 01:56.077
Mary: DO YOU KNOW WHAT
KILLED NEARLY EVERY
WOMAN BURIED HERE? LOVE.

01:56.110 --> 01:58.670
Cotton: AND WITCHES ARMED
WITH DEADLY MALICE...

01:58.710 --> 02:01.417
Mary: MOST DIED IN CHILDBIRTH.
SO LOVE IS TO A WOMAN...

02:01.450 --> 02:03.782
Cotton: ...ARE THE MOST
MALIGNANT AND INSIDIOUS
WEAPONS IN THAT BATTLE...

02:03.820 --> 02:05.117
Mary:
...WHAT WAR IS TO A MAN.

02:05.150 --> 02:06.754
THE MOST DEADLY THING,
THEY'LL DO.

02:06.790 --> 02:08.257
Cotton: ...THAT WAR FOR THE BODY
AND THE SOUL OF A NATION.

02:08.290 --> 02:10.679
Mary: ONLY A FOOL RUNS
QUICKLY TO WAR...

02:10.730 --> 02:12.129
Cotton:
IMAGINE A FOE YOU CAN'T SEE...

02:12.160 --> 02:13.525
-Mary: ...OR LOVE.
-Cotton: ...ARMED WITH

02:13.560 --> 02:15.027
-WEAPONS UNKNOWN...
-Mary: I CAN TEACH YOU...

02:15.060 --> 02:17.665
Cotton: ...AND THE ABILITY
TO APPEAR AS ANYONE.

02:17.700 --> 02:20.589
Mary: ...ABOUT LIFE AND DEATH
AND MANY THINGS IN BETWEEN.

02:20.640 --> 02:23.131
Anne: STOP IT!
JUST STOP IT! STOP.

02:23.170 --> 02:25.536
John:Shh.

02:25.570 --> 02:27.333
JUDGE NOT, LEST YE BE JUDGED.

02:29.480 --> 02:31.368
Anne: [ GASPS ]

02:43.430 --> 02:45.523
[ WATER SPLASHES ]

02:58.840 --> 03:01.206
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

03:15.460 --> 03:17.121
[ "CUPID CARRIES A GUN" PLAYS ]

03:23.130 --> 03:25.860
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:25.900 --> 03:27.436
* WITCH DRUMS

03:27.470 --> 03:30.109
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:31.370 --> 03:33.930
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:33.980 --> 03:35.379
* THE WITCH DRUMS

03:35.410 --> 03:37.947
* BETTER PRAY FOR HELL

03:37.980 --> 03:43.282
* NOT HALLELUJAH

04:01.500 --> 04:03.502
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

04:10.510 --> 04:12.774
Man: BURN IN HELL!

04:12.820 --> 04:14.970
[ SHOUTING CONTINUES ]

04:16.850 --> 04:18.249
Woman: SIN!

04:18.290 --> 04:19.780
Isaac:
BE ASSURED, MRS. BRIDGET --

04:19.820 --> 04:21.287
ONES THAT ARE WEEPIN'

04:21.320 --> 04:23.584
FAR OUTNUMBER THE ONES
THAT MIGHT SPIT OR CURSE.

04:23.630 --> 04:25.484
Man: BURN IN HELL! BURN!

04:25.530 --> 04:27.452
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

04:27.500 --> 04:29.468
Tituba: YOU WOULD DO WELL
TO PAY THAT BOY EXTRA

04:29.500 --> 04:32.992
TO TAKE THEM BODIES
A MORE CIRCUITOUS ROUTE.

04:33.040 --> 04:36.339
Mary: SPECTACLE
IS FUEL FOR OUR FIRE.

04:36.370 --> 04:40.079
Tituba: AND DOUBT IS INDULGED
BY THE RICH AND SPOILED ONLY.

04:40.110 --> 04:42.977
MIND THAT YOU WAS BORN NEITHER.

04:46.180 --> 04:50.139
Woman: "GIVE ME TO DIE WITH THEE
THAT I MAY RISE TO A NEW LIFE,

04:50.190 --> 04:53.353
"FOR I WISH TO BE AS DEAD
AND BURIED TO SIN,

04:53.390 --> 04:54.652
TO SELFISHNESS..."

04:54.690 --> 04:56.351
Mary:
BY ALL MEANS, REVEREND --

04:56.390 --> 05:00.019
DO NOT OFFER PRAYER OR COMFORT
OR WORDS OF ENCOURAGEMENT.

05:00.060 --> 05:03.359
NO, STAND AS A BEWILDERED STATUE
AMONGST THE PEOPLE OF SALEM

05:03.400 --> 05:05.994
AND OFFER THEM
ABSOLUTELY NOTHING.

05:06.030 --> 05:08.339
Cotton:
WHAT WOULD YOU HAVE ME DO?

05:08.370 --> 05:10.634
Mary:
WHAT I BROUGHT YOU HERE TO DO.

05:10.670 --> 05:13.935
GUIDE AND SUPPORT US
IN OUR GREAT HOUR OF NEED.

05:13.980 --> 05:16.369
WARM OUR HEARTS
WITH YOUR WORDS OF WISDOM.

05:16.410 --> 05:19.538
ASSURE US IT IS GOD'S WILL WE DO
IN FERRETING OUT THE DEVIL.

05:19.580 --> 05:22.048
OR AT THE VERY, VERY LEAST...

05:22.080 --> 05:24.184
PRAY.

05:26.320 --> 05:27.514
Mr. Hale: TRAGIC DAY.

05:27.560 --> 05:29.380
Mary: TRAGIC BUT NECESSARY.

05:29.430 --> 05:32.399
Mr. Hale:
TRAGICALLY NECESSARY.

05:32.430 --> 05:35.319
SURELY, THE GRIEVING
OF THE MASSES GIVES YOU PAUSE.

05:35.360 --> 05:36.827
Mary: MOST SPIT AND CURSE

05:36.870 --> 05:38.667
WHILE SUMMONING
THE BURNING FLAMES OF HELL.

05:38.700 --> 05:40.190
Mr. Hale:
THERE ARE ALSO THOSE

05:40.240 --> 05:43.403
WHO WEEP FOR HER
AND FIND HER HANGING UNFOUNDED.

05:43.440 --> 05:45.658
Mary: NOT ENOUGH
TO DIVERT OUR INTENTIONS.

05:45.710 --> 05:49.077
A PANIC'S SUCCESS RELIES
ON ITS ESCALATION.

05:49.110 --> 05:51.249
THE GRAND RITE HAS BEGUN.

05:51.280 --> 05:53.214
WE LOOK TO OUR NEXT VICTIM.

05:53.250 --> 05:54.717
Mr. Hale: AND THATI DISAGREE,

05:54.750 --> 05:57.218
THAT I STRENUOUSLY
AND MOST VEHEMENTLY OPPOSE

05:57.250 --> 05:58.547
MEANS NOTHING TO YOU?

05:58.590 --> 06:01.753
WE WERE SEEN AT OUR SABBAT.

06:01.790 --> 06:03.929
AND YOU THROW CAUTION
TO THE WIND.

06:05.130 --> 06:07.052
Mary: AND HAVE YOU IDENTIFIED
WHO SAW US?

06:10.200 --> 06:12.589
PERHAPS YOUR DISAGREEMENTS
AND VEHEMENT OPPOSITION

06:12.640 --> 06:14.995
MIGHT HOLD MORE WEIGHT
IF YOU COULD BE RELIED ON

06:15.040 --> 06:17.861
TO COMPLETE A SIMPLE TASK.

06:17.910 --> 06:20.435
GOOD DAY, HALE.

06:25.480 --> 06:27.118
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

06:27.150 --> 06:30.381
Cotton:
WHAT MUST I DO TO BE SAVED?

06:30.420 --> 06:33.753
IT IS IMPOSSIBLE TO ASK
A MORE WEIGHTY QUESTION.

06:33.790 --> 06:37.453
LEST WE PERISH ETERNALLY.

06:37.490 --> 06:39.799
John: HOW DOES IT FEEL?

06:39.830 --> 06:41.752
Cotton: HOW DOES WHAT FEEL?

06:41.800 --> 06:44.598
John: KILLING TWO INNOCENTS
IN AS MANY DAYS.

06:44.630 --> 06:46.393
Cotton: THE EVIDENCE
AGAINST MISS BISHOP --

06:46.440 --> 06:49.261
Woman: THE ORPHANAGE! HELP!
THEY'RE LOOTING THE ORPHANAGE!

06:49.300 --> 06:51.029
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

06:51.070 --> 06:52.935
Anne: GIVE IT BACK!

06:52.980 --> 06:54.629
IT'S NOT YOURS!

06:54.680 --> 06:56.648
[ BABY CRYING ]

06:56.680 --> 06:58.170
GIVE IT --

06:59.980 --> 07:03.279
John:
NEXT ONE'S TO YOUR HEAD.

07:03.320 --> 07:05.686
[ CHILDREN CRYING ]

07:10.530 --> 07:12.157
ARE YOU OKAY?

07:12.190 --> 07:14.658
Anne:
IT'S AWFUL. IT'S TOO AWFUL.

07:14.700 --> 07:16.099
Mr. Hale: W-WHAT'S HAPPENED?

07:16.130 --> 07:17.722
John: THIEVES HAVE COME
TO RANSACK THE ORPHANAGE

07:17.770 --> 07:19.761
NOW THAT THE TOWN SEES FIT
TO HANG ITS GUARDIAN.

07:19.800 --> 07:21.165
Mr. Hale: EASY, SON.

07:21.200 --> 07:22.963
John: THIS IS WHAT COMES
OF YOUR WITCH PANIC.

07:23.010 --> 07:24.102
Mr. Hale: ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

07:24.140 --> 07:26.472
Anne: THIS IS YOUR FAULT!
AND HIS.

07:26.510 --> 07:29.308
Mr. Hale: [ SIGHS ] FORGIVE HER.
SHE'S DISTRAUGHT.

07:29.340 --> 07:30.841
Anne: I'M RIGHT!

07:30.880 --> 07:33.644
SEE ME HOME.

07:40.820 --> 07:42.685
Mr. Hale: CAPTAIN,
IF YOU WOULDN'T MIND, HMM?

07:42.730 --> 07:45.290
John: YES. OF COURSE.

07:51.000 --> 07:53.389
Anne:
WHERE HAVE THEY TAKEN HER?

07:54.870 --> 07:57.668
John: FOUL SPOT
WHERE THEY REST THE UNWANTED.

08:00.540 --> 08:01.973
Anne: IS IT VERY TERRIBLE?

08:03.910 --> 08:06.105
John: YES.

08:06.150 --> 08:08.948
[ BELL TOLLING ]

08:08.980 --> 08:11.448
Anne: THANK YOU...

08:11.490 --> 08:14.982
FOR YOUR HEROISM
AND YOUR CANDOR.

08:21.730 --> 08:24.096
[ HORSE WHINNIES ]

08:34.110 --> 08:36.237
[ DOOR OPENS ]

08:39.550 --> 08:42.986
Petrus: [ LAUGHS ]
WELCOME, WELCOME, WELCOME!

08:43.020 --> 08:44.419
A CUP OF TEA?

08:44.450 --> 08:46.418
-A TOUCH OF PORT?
-Mr. Hale: NO TIME.

08:46.450 --> 08:49.055
WHO SAW US IN THE WOODS?

08:49.090 --> 08:53.550
Petrus:
IT WAS...HE WHO IS MARKED.

08:53.600 --> 08:57.161
HE OF THE "F"
THAT FURROWS HIS BROW.

08:57.200 --> 08:59.361
-Mr. Hale: ISAAC?
-Petrus: THE FORNICATOR.

08:59.400 --> 09:00.697
Mr. Hale: THE IDIOT.

09:02.970 --> 09:04.858
Petrus: ONE MORE THING.

09:05.940 --> 09:07.976
ISAAC WAS NOT ALONE.

09:09.710 --> 09:11.598
Mr. Hale:
WHO ELSE WAS WITH HIM?

09:11.650 --> 09:13.914
Petrus: I DON'T KNOW.

09:13.950 --> 09:15.611
I COULD NOT MAKE OUT THE FACE.

09:15.650 --> 09:17.117
Mr. Hale: YOU DON'T KNOW.

09:17.150 --> 09:19.118
WHAT GOOD ARE YOU?

09:19.150 --> 09:20.959
A SEER WHO CAN'T SEE.

09:20.990 --> 09:23.254
Petrus:
IT'S NOT AN EXACT ART.

09:23.290 --> 09:26.555
Mr. Hale: EVIDENTLY NOT.

09:26.600 --> 09:28.488
Petrus: [ CHUCKLES ]

10:00.500 --> 10:02.024
John: HELLO?

10:14.680 --> 10:15.999
[ METAL SCRAPING ]

10:30.190 --> 10:32.181
[ CROW CAWS ]

10:32.230 --> 10:33.527
HELLO?

10:44.710 --> 10:46.735
[ DOG GROWLING ]

10:54.420 --> 10:55.978
[ SNARLING ]

11:07.060 --> 11:08.550
[ GRUNTS ]

11:08.600 --> 11:10.124
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

11:17.540 --> 11:19.667
John:
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT PLACE?

11:19.710 --> 11:22.406
Mr. Hale:
THE SHACK BELONGS TO PETRUS,

11:22.440 --> 11:26.001
AN EXPERT ON CREATURES
BOTH FERAL AND OTHERWISE.

11:26.050 --> 11:29.417
John: YEAH, WELL, THEY LOOKED
DEAD...UNTIL THEY DIDN'T.

11:30.950 --> 11:32.645
Mr. Hale: NO DEAD ANIMAL

11:32.690 --> 11:35.181
COULD THREATEN A STORIED SOLDIER
SUCH AS YOURSELF, CAPTAIN.

11:35.220 --> 11:39.259
John: IT COULD, IF POWERED
BY FORCES WE DON'T UNDERSTAND.

11:39.290 --> 11:41.019
-Mr. Hale: SUCH AS?
-John: WITCHCRAFI'.

11:41.060 --> 11:42.698
-Mr. Hale: NONSENSE.
-John: IS IT?

11:42.730 --> 11:44.595
YOU KNOW HIM WELL, THIS PETRUS?

11:44.630 --> 11:47.599
Mr. Hale: YOU'LL FIND NO MAN
MORE ORDINARY THAN PETRUS.

11:47.640 --> 11:49.938
TO SAY THAT HE'S MUNDANE
IS TO OVERSTATE HIS PASSION.

11:49.970 --> 11:52.609
John: AND WHAT ORDINARY TASK
BROUGHT YOU DEEP INTO THE FOREST

11:52.640 --> 11:54.232
TO SEEK HIS MUNDANE COUNSEL?

11:54.280 --> 11:55.577
Mr. Hale: EASY, SON...

11:55.610 --> 11:58.340
OR I MIGHT SUSPECT
YOUR PRESENCE HERE

11:58.380 --> 12:00.439
AS MORE THAN A COINCIDENCE,

12:00.480 --> 12:02.675
THAT, PERHAPS,
FOR REASONS OF YOUR OWN

12:02.720 --> 12:06.087
ABOUT WHICH I'M SURE
YOU'D RATHER I NOT INQUIRE,

12:06.120 --> 12:08.281
YOU MIGHT HAVE FOLLOWED ME HERE.

12:08.320 --> 12:11.050
AND WHAT A SHAME...

12:11.090 --> 12:12.796
TO HAVE SUSPICION
OVERTAKE THE GRACE I OWE

12:12.830 --> 12:16.459
FOR THE KINDNESS
YOU SHOWED MY DAUGHTER.

12:16.500 --> 12:18.718
John: CONSIDER IT REPAID.

12:18.770 --> 12:20.829
Mr. Hale: GOOD.

12:22.500 --> 12:24.604
George: [ GAGGING ]

12:37.020 --> 12:40.251
Mary: GEORGE, REALLY.

12:40.290 --> 12:44.283
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU ARE WORSE THAN A CHILD.

12:44.330 --> 12:45.729
George: [ GROANS ]

12:45.760 --> 12:47.921
Mary: HE SERVES AT MY BEHEST,
NOT YOURS.

12:47.960 --> 12:49.496
HE WON'T COME OUT FOR YOU.

12:49.530 --> 12:51.669
OHH.

12:51.700 --> 12:54.294
THERE, THERE, LITTLE MAN.

12:54.340 --> 12:56.808
OH, PAY THE BEAST NO MIND.

12:56.840 --> 13:00.401
REST NOW, AND I'LL SEE
TO YOUR FEEDING LATER.

13:00.440 --> 13:03.500
Tituba: ISAAC'S BRUNG
THE MASTER'S POTIONS.

13:03.550 --> 13:04.949
Mary: TELL HIM TO WAIT.

13:06.210 --> 13:07.472
[ SIGHS ]

13:07.520 --> 13:09.476
OHH, GEORGE.

13:09.520 --> 13:13.559
YOUR NIGHTDRESS
THOROUGHLY DRENCHED IN SICK.

13:14.860 --> 13:17.351
STEW IN THAT FOR THE DAY,
MY SWEET.

13:17.390 --> 13:19.381
George: [ GURGLES ]

13:23.370 --> 13:24.667
Isaac: FOR MR. SIBLEY.

13:24.700 --> 13:26.190
Mary:
OH, AND NOT A MOMENT TOO SOON.

13:26.230 --> 13:28.039
JUST NOW,
HE SUFFERED A FIT OF SORTS.

13:28.070 --> 13:30.209
Isaac: IF YOU DON'T MIND ME
SAYING SO, MA'AM,

13:30.240 --> 13:31.867
IT'S A BURDEN YOU'VE TOOK ON --

13:31.910 --> 13:34.504
A BURDEN AND LOAD, CARRIED OUT
WITHOUT CRY OR COMPLAINT.

13:35.980 --> 13:39.347
Mary: MY BURDENS CAN'T COMPARE
TO THAT OF SALEM ITSELF.

13:39.380 --> 13:41.519
HOW DO YOU FIND THE SPIRITS
ON THE SQUARE?

13:41.550 --> 13:44.713
Isaac:
LOW, MA'AM. AWFUL LOW.

13:45.920 --> 13:47.558
Mary: PERHAPS THERE IS SOLACE
TO BE FOUND

13:47.590 --> 13:50.753
IN REMEMBRANCE OF TIMES WHEN
WE'VE BOTH SHOULDERED WORSE.

14:02.440 --> 14:04.362
WHO COULD HAVE IMAGINED
THAT A SINGLE NIGHT

14:04.410 --> 14:07.174
COULD HAVE CONSEQUENCE
FOR SO MANY?

14:07.210 --> 14:08.973
NOT ALL SCARS CAN BE SEEN.

14:09.010 --> 14:11.501
BUT THEY EXIST NONETHELESS.

14:17.920 --> 14:19.740
Isaac:
NEXT MORNING, SHE WAS GONE.

14:19.790 --> 14:22.554
RUN AWAY AND DISAPPEARED.

14:22.590 --> 14:25.525
Mary: OH, YOUR SWEET ABBY.

14:27.030 --> 14:28.725
Isaac: I'LL ADMIT
TO WONDERING ON OCCASION

14:28.760 --> 14:32.560
WHAT IT MIGHT BE LIKE
TO ONE DAY SEE HER AGAIN

14:32.600 --> 14:35.933
OR KNOW OF HER OR HEAR HER FATE.

14:35.970 --> 14:38.530
WOULD IT BE BETTER
OR SO MUCH WORSE?

14:42.280 --> 14:45.272
Mary:
I CAN ASSURE YOU, ISAAC --

14:45.310 --> 14:46.868
IF YOU WERE TO SEE HER AGAIN,

14:46.920 --> 14:49.514
YOU WOULD FIND THOSE FEELINGS
BURIED TOO DEEPLY

14:49.550 --> 14:51.541
FOR HOPE OF RESURRECTION.

14:55.660 --> 14:57.059
GOOD AFTERNOON, ISAAC.

14:57.090 --> 14:59.149
Isaac: G'DAY, MA'AM.

15:04.600 --> 15:06.591
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

15:30.660 --> 15:32.628
AAH!

15:32.660 --> 15:34.924
[ GRUNTING ]

15:42.870 --> 15:44.599
[ INSECTS BUZZING ]

15:54.720 --> 15:56.676
WHAT IS THAT?

15:56.720 --> 15:59.314
WHAT IS THAT?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

16:00.220 --> 16:02.256
PLEASE. PLEASE.

16:02.290 --> 16:05.726
[ MUFFLED SCREAMING ]

16:22.240 --> 16:24.242
[ GASPS ]

16:28.250 --> 16:30.411
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

16:32.890 --> 16:36.018
Pigman: WHAT DID YOU SEE
IN THE WOODS?

16:36.060 --> 16:37.982
Isaac: [ SCREAMS ]

16:38.030 --> 16:41.227
Pigman:
WE KNEW YOU WEREN'T ALONE.

16:41.260 --> 16:43.626
Woman: WE KNOW!

16:43.670 --> 16:47.197
WE KNOW! WE KNOW!

16:47.240 --> 16:49.128
Isaac: [ CRIES ]

16:49.170 --> 16:52.367
Woman: WHO WAS THERE?!
WHO WAS THERE?!

16:52.410 --> 16:54.628
Isaac: I WAS ALONE!

16:54.680 --> 16:56.705
I WAS ALONE!

17:01.350 --> 17:03.215
Mr. Hale: GET IT ALL.

17:03.250 --> 17:04.512
WANT NO TRACE OF OUR EFFORTS.

17:04.550 --> 17:06.643
THE FAULT MUST LIE
WITH HIM ALONE.

17:06.690 --> 17:08.487
[ CROW CAWS ]

17:08.520 --> 17:11.683
AND PUT THESE IN HIS POCKETS.

17:11.730 --> 17:13.049
IF HE'S TO BE FOUND A WITCH,

17:13.100 --> 17:16.194
THE GOOD REVEREND
WILL REQUIRE PROOF...

17:18.570 --> 17:22.131
...EVIDENCE TO SEAL HIS FATE,
HMM?

17:23.640 --> 17:25.232
WHAT IS IT?

17:25.270 --> 17:27.602
IS THIS SYMPATHY
THAT I'M SENSING?

17:27.640 --> 17:29.608
ONE OUTCAST TO THE OTHER?

17:29.640 --> 17:32.871
IS THAT WHAT YOU FEEL,
YOU DECREPIT DEFORMITY?

17:34.750 --> 17:36.115
Ghoul: MARY!

17:36.150 --> 17:38.243
Mr. Hale: SO NOW EVEN YOU
WOULD QUESTION ME?

17:38.290 --> 17:39.985
DO AS YOU'RE TOLD!

17:45.130 --> 17:47.621
DOES YOUR GREAT MARY KNOW WHAT
IT IS TO WATCH WITCHES BURN?

17:49.800 --> 17:51.222
NOTHING OF THE OLD WAYS

17:51.270 --> 17:53.864
WHILE SHE'S WHIPPING US
TOWARD THE NEW.

17:53.900 --> 17:58.030
A SPELL OF VITAE CUPIDO,

17:58.070 --> 18:00.277
AND THEN WE SEND HIM
TO THE ONE PLACE IN TOWN

18:00.310 --> 18:04.076
THAT WILL CERTAINLY
DENY HIM ENTRANCE.

18:04.110 --> 18:06.408
THAT SHOULD GET THEIR ATTENTION.

18:18.190 --> 18:20.192
Gloriana: [ SNIFFLES ]

18:22.630 --> 18:23.927
Cotton: YOU'RE CRYING.

18:23.970 --> 18:25.597
Gloriana:
[ Chuckling ] I'M NOT.

18:27.370 --> 18:28.667
Cotton: YOU ARE.

18:29.870 --> 18:31.508
WHAT'S WRONG?

18:31.540 --> 18:34.771
Gloriana: IF THEY CAN HANG
A WOMAN LIKE MISS BISHOP,

18:34.810 --> 18:37.199
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN
FOR SOMEONE LIKE ME?

18:38.950 --> 18:40.975
Cotton: NOTHING
IS GOING TO HAPPEN TO YOU.

18:41.020 --> 18:43.341
Gloriana:
HOW CAN YOU BE SO SURE?

18:43.390 --> 18:46.279
JUST YESTERDAY, IT WAS ME THAT
THEY PUT BEFORE THE LEWIS GIRL.

18:47.620 --> 18:49.656
WOULD YOU HAVE COME FORWARD
HAD I BEEN ACCUSED?

18:49.690 --> 18:51.521
Cotton:
I FOLLOW EVERY PROTOCOL.

18:51.560 --> 18:55.951
I ADHERE TO EVERY LETTER
OF WHAT MY FATHER TAUGHT ME.

18:56.000 --> 19:01.063
NO ONE IS CONVICTED WITHOUT
INCONTROVERTIBLE EVIDENCE.

19:04.040 --> 19:06.907
Gloriana: SO YOU'RE CERTAIN
MISS BISHOP WAS A WITCH?

19:09.810 --> 19:12.176
Cotton: I'M CERTAIN...

19:12.210 --> 19:13.711
OF THE EVIDENCE.

19:23.530 --> 19:25.725
Gloriana: WHY DO YOU DO IT?

19:27.060 --> 19:29.153
Cotton: WHY?

19:31.100 --> 19:33.660
Gloriana: IS IT THAT YOU BELIEVE
THAT YOU'RE DOING GOOD?

19:35.570 --> 19:39.199
OR IS IT THAT YOU WISH
TO PLEASE YOUR FATHER?

19:41.280 --> 19:43.077
[ SCREAMING, GLASS SHATTERING ]

19:50.950 --> 19:52.019
Gloriana:
IT'S ISAAC! HE'S MAD!

19:53.690 --> 19:54.918
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

19:54.960 --> 19:56.757
[ SCREAMING CONTINUES ]

19:56.790 --> 19:59.384
Cotton:
I CAN'T BE SEEN HERE.

20:04.270 --> 20:06.761
Isaac: [ LAUGHS ]
LET ME TOUCH YOU!

20:06.800 --> 20:09.098
[ WOMEN SCREAMING ]

20:09.140 --> 20:10.801
GET UP!

20:12.910 --> 20:14.400
Woman: ISAAC, NO!

20:14.440 --> 20:16.237
Isaac: HA HA! AH HA HA!

20:16.280 --> 20:17.577
[ WOMEN SCREAMING ]

20:27.390 --> 20:29.255
Isaac:
[ LAUGHING MANIACALLY]

20:29.290 --> 20:32.953
[ ISAAC SCREAMING ]

20:34.930 --> 20:36.124
Gloriana:
ISAAC, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

20:36.160 --> 20:38.594
Isaac: WHAT DO YOU SEE?!

20:38.630 --> 20:40.097
Cotton: ISAAC!

20:40.130 --> 20:41.961
-Isaac: OH, THERE YOU ARE!
-Cotton: ISAAC!

20:42.000 --> 20:43.900
[ WOMEN SCREAMING ]

20:49.180 --> 20:52.809
Isaac: ISAAC THE FORNICATOR!
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR!

20:52.850 --> 20:55.239
HIDE YOUR WIVES!
HIDE ALL YOUR SHEEP!

20:55.280 --> 20:58.488
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR
WILL GET THEM WHEN THEY SLEEP!

20:58.520 --> 21:00.283
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR!

21:00.320 --> 21:02.311
HIDE YOUR WIVES!
HIDE YOUR WIVES!

21:02.360 --> 21:04.123
HIDE ALL YOUR SHEEP!

21:04.160 --> 21:06.981
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR!
HIDE YOUR WIVES!

21:07.030 --> 21:08.588
John: ISAAC!

21:08.630 --> 21:09.949
Isaac: HIDE YOUR SHEEP.
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR.

21:10.000 --> 21:11.490
John: STOP! ISAAC!

21:11.530 --> 21:13.259
Isaac: JONATHAN, IT'S NO GOOD.
IT'S NO GOOD!

21:13.300 --> 21:14.494
John: WHAT IS NO GOOD?

21:14.540 --> 21:16.292
Isaac: THEY SAW US.
THEY SAW US.

21:16.340 --> 21:19.503
THEY SAW US IN THE WOODS.
THEY SAW US.

21:21.710 --> 21:23.132
THEY SAW US IN THE WOODS.
THEY SAW US.

21:23.180 --> 21:24.442
John: SHUT UP.

21:24.480 --> 21:26.277
Mr. Hale:
TAKE HIM TO THE JAIL.

21:26.310 --> 21:27.516
Isaac:
THEY SAW US IN THE WOODS.

21:27.550 --> 21:28.812
-THEY SAW US.
-John: Shh.

21:39.190 --> 21:40.498
Mary: MAGISTRATE.

21:40.530 --> 21:41.792
Mr. Hale: MRS. SIBLEY.

21:41.830 --> 21:43.149
Mary: WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

21:43.200 --> 21:45.964
Mr. Hale:
THE IDIOT SAW US IN THE WOODS.

21:46.000 --> 21:47.365
Mary: ISAAC.

21:47.400 --> 21:50.528
SO, YOU DID THIS
WITHOUT CONSENT?

21:50.570 --> 21:52.800
Mr. Hale: HE WASN'T ALONE.

21:52.840 --> 21:55.172
WE'LL FIND OUT WHO WAS WITH HIM,
AND HE WILL BURN.

21:55.210 --> 21:57.098
Mary: NO, YOU WILL DO
NOTHING FURTHER.

21:57.140 --> 21:58.471
-Mr. Hale: WHAT?
-Mary: NOTHING!

21:58.510 --> 22:00.000
GO HOME, MAGISTRATE.

22:00.050 --> 22:02.245
YOU REEK OF THE WOODS.

22:03.690 --> 22:05.487
[ HORSE NEIGHS ]

22:08.860 --> 22:11.158
FIND ME ROSE.

22:15.060 --> 22:17.199
Isaac: [ GROANS ]

22:17.230 --> 22:19.562
John:
A DRUNKEN ROMP, THAT'S ALL --

22:19.600 --> 22:21.329
A YOUNG MAN'S PREROGATIVE.

22:21.370 --> 22:23.634
Cotton: AND YET
NO SMELL OF SPIRITS ON HIM.

22:23.670 --> 22:25.706
John: OH, WELL, BURN HIM, THEN.
WHY WAIT?

22:25.740 --> 22:28.379
Cotton: IF HE WAS SPELLED,
HE'S BLAMELESS IN HIS ACTIONS.

22:28.410 --> 22:30.549
John:
YET YOU STILL HOLD HIM. WHY?

22:30.580 --> 22:33.640
Cotton:
FOUND ON HIS PERSON.

22:33.680 --> 22:37.548
LIKELY STOLEN TO CAST A SPELL
ON ITS OWNER.

22:37.590 --> 22:40.218
John: ONE MINUTE, HE'S SPELLER.
THE NEXT, HE'S BEWITCHED.

22:40.250 --> 22:41.581
MAKE UP YOUR MIND, REVEREND.

22:41.620 --> 22:46.080
IS HE A WITCH
OR A VICTIM OF THE CRAFT?

22:46.130 --> 22:48.428
Cotton: CHIEF INGREDIENT
OF A WITCH'S BREW.

22:48.460 --> 22:51.566
John:
ISAAC TOOK ME INTO THOSE WOODS.

22:51.600 --> 22:53.227
HE RISKED HIS LIFE
TO SHOW ME THE WITCHES.

22:53.270 --> 22:54.897
WHY, IF HE WAS ONE?

22:54.940 --> 22:57.033
Lamb:
I'VE, UH, ADMINISTRATED A TONIC

22:57.070 --> 23:00.733
THAT'LL SETTLE HIM DOWN
AND, UH, END THE FITS.

23:00.780 --> 23:03.169
Cotton: WHAT IS YOUR SURGEON'S
OPINION OF THE BOY'S CONDITION?

23:03.210 --> 23:06.077
Lamb: I CAN'T SAY FOR SURE
AS TO CAUSE OR SOURCE,

23:06.110 --> 23:09.511
BUT GOING BY HIS BABBLE,
THAT BOY IS GOOD AND TOUCHED.

23:09.550 --> 23:12.587
Mr. Hale:
EVERY BENEFIT OF THE DOUBT,

23:12.620 --> 23:14.918
EVERY AVENUE EXPLORED.

23:14.960 --> 23:16.757
THE BOY IS ONE OF OUR OWN.

23:16.790 --> 23:18.087
OUTCAST AND SHUNNED
AS HE MAY BE,

23:18.130 --> 23:20.519
HE STILL RESIDES
IN THE BOSOM OF SALEM.

23:20.560 --> 23:22.255
I'LL, UH --

23:22.300 --> 23:24.097
I'LL SPEAK WITH HIM PERSONALLY.

23:24.130 --> 23:25.768
Lamb: [ LAUGHS]
NOT TONIGHT, YOU WON'T.

23:25.800 --> 23:27.358
Mr. Hale: AND WHY NOT?

23:27.400 --> 23:29.960
John: LAMB GAVE ISAAC A TONIC
TO HELP HIM SLEEP.

23:30.000 --> 23:32.036
[ HORSE NEIGHS ]

23:32.070 --> 23:34.630
Cotton:
PROBABLY BEST, MAGISTRATE,
TO RETURN IN THE MORNING.

23:34.680 --> 23:36.272
John: YES, MAGISTRATE.

23:36.310 --> 23:38.904
YOU CAN HAVE YOUR PERSONAL TALK
WITH HIM THEN.

24:06.310 --> 24:10.804
Mary:
ROSE, ABSENT THE MAGISTRATE,

24:10.850 --> 24:14.172
WHAT CHANCE HAVE I OF HARNESSING
THE BODY'S ALLEGIANCE?

24:14.220 --> 24:16.711
Rose: [ SIGHS ]

24:17.890 --> 24:20.518
THE OTHERS ARE SPLIT
BETWEEN OLD AND NEW.

24:20.560 --> 24:23.120
DIFFICULT TO PREDICT THE OUTCOME
OF SUCH A DIVIDE.

24:23.160 --> 24:24.923
Mary: YOU'RE OLD

24:24.960 --> 24:27.349
AND YET SOMEHOW NOT GOVERNED
BY THIS FEAR.

24:27.390 --> 24:30.826
Rose: IT IS NOT AGE
THAT DIVIDES US, BUT AMBITION.

24:30.870 --> 24:34.169
Mary: [ CHUCKLES]
WELL, HE'S NOT WITHOUT AMBITION.

24:34.200 --> 24:36.589
Rose: IT CHAFES HIM
TO BEND TO A WOMAN,

24:36.640 --> 24:40.462
BUT HE DOES SO THAT
OUR GREATER PURPOSE MAY LIVE.

24:40.510 --> 24:42.034
Mary:
IT WAS TO BE ME THAT LED US.

24:42.080 --> 24:43.843
Rose: IT WAS AND IT IS.

24:43.880 --> 24:46.178
Mary: QUESTIONED AND CHALLENGED
AT EVERY TURN,

24:46.210 --> 24:49.714
EACH AND EVERY DECISION
SOLICITING DOUBT AND SCRUTINY.

24:49.750 --> 24:51.479
Rose:
MUCH AS WE MAY WISH IT,

24:51.520 --> 24:54.512
PRIMACY DOES NOT LIVE
IN THE ABYSS.

24:57.860 --> 25:00.021
Mary: IT CANNOT HAVE
ALL BEEN IN VAIN.

25:02.200 --> 25:03.428
Rose: SIBLEY.

25:08.070 --> 25:09.935
YOUR BABY.

25:11.740 --> 25:15.528
Mary: IT CANNOT HAVE
ALL BEEN IN VAIN.

25:17.580 --> 25:21.414
THIS LIFE, MY...

25:21.450 --> 25:23.475
Rose: CHOICES.

25:23.520 --> 25:25.715
Mary: WAS THERE A CHOICE?

25:25.750 --> 25:28.218
OR WAS CHOICE TAKEN FROM ME?

25:28.260 --> 25:33.357
Rose: IT'S TOO LATE NOW
TO THINK OF SUCH THINGS.

25:33.390 --> 25:35.927
Mary: IS IT?

25:42.400 --> 25:46.063
Rose: IT MUSTN'T HAVE BEEN EASY
SEEING HIM AGAIN.

25:53.980 --> 25:55.914
IT IS YOURS TO DECIDE, MY GIRL,

25:55.950 --> 25:59.579
WHAT IS IN VAIN AND WHAT IS NOT.

25:59.620 --> 26:02.453
Mary: AND YOU WILL STAND
BEHIND MY DECISION?

26:03.790 --> 26:05.621
Rose: UP TO A POINT.

26:05.660 --> 26:08.925
Mary: HMM.

26:08.960 --> 26:11.292
Rose:
THE MAGISTER'S ROOTS ARE OLD.

26:11.330 --> 26:14.197
HE HAS SEEN MUCH
AND SUFFERED GREATLY.

26:14.240 --> 26:17.164
DO NOT UNDERESTIMATE HIM.

26:23.010 --> 26:25.103
[THUNDER RUMBLES ]

26:25.150 --> 26:27.277
John: MRS. SIBLEY.

26:27.310 --> 26:28.709
Mary: CAPTAIN ALDEN.

26:28.750 --> 26:30.445
John: ISAAC IS NOT A WITCH.

26:30.480 --> 26:32.539
YOU DO NOTHING,
HE'LL BE HUNG FOR ONE.

26:32.590 --> 26:35.286
WE HAVE TO STOP THIS.

26:39.490 --> 26:42.459
THERE'S NOTHING LEFT IN YOU.

26:42.500 --> 26:46.288
NO FEELINGS, NO HEART.

26:46.330 --> 26:48.798
YOU'RE NOT THE GIRL I ONCE KNEW.

26:50.100 --> 26:52.330
Mary:
HAVE THEY QUESTIONED HIM?

26:54.440 --> 26:55.998
John: NO.

26:56.040 --> 26:58.247
THAT'S BECAUSE HE WAS GIVEN
A SLEEPING TONIC.

26:58.280 --> 27:01.010
Mary:
SO HE'S SAID NOTHING.

27:02.550 --> 27:03.812
John: NOTHING.

27:03.850 --> 27:05.249
COTTON IS EAGER,

27:05.290 --> 27:06.917
AND THE MAGISTRATE
WAS HARD TO TURN AWAY.

27:06.950 --> 27:09.282
Mary: HALE? WAS THERE?

27:09.320 --> 27:11.527
John: HE CAME STRAIGHT
TO QUESTION HIM.

27:14.500 --> 27:17.719
Mary: YOU HAVE
MY COMPLETE ALLEGIANCE.

27:21.740 --> 27:23.708
[ HORSE NEIGHS ]

27:25.140 --> 27:29.372
Cotton: "OUR OPPORTUNITIES
TO DO GOOD ARE OUR TALENTS."

27:29.410 --> 27:31.878
MY FATHER SAID THAT.

27:31.910 --> 27:35.676
THE GREAT INCREASE MATHER.

27:35.720 --> 27:41.056
TO STAY IM PARTIAL,
TO WEIGH WITHOUT BIAS --

27:41.090 --> 27:44.878
IS THIS THE GOOD
I'M MEANT TO DO?

27:46.390 --> 27:50.759
I DON'T WANT YOUR LIFE
IN MY HANDS.

27:52.370 --> 27:56.397
HALF OF SALEM TAKES YOU
FOR A FOOL.

27:56.440 --> 27:59.238
THE REST DISMISS YOU
AS A PERVERT.

27:59.270 --> 28:01.534
AM I MAD TO THINK
I SAW SOMETHING IN YOU?

28:01.580 --> 28:04.105
SOMETHING OF A MAN?

28:06.280 --> 28:08.840
JUST THE SORT SALEM NEEDS
TO FIGHT THE DEVIL.

28:08.880 --> 28:10.370
[THUNDER RUMBLES ]

28:10.420 --> 28:13.412
Abigail: [ Echoing ]
ISAAC, ISAAC. ISAAC.

28:17.760 --> 28:20.024
OH, SWEET ISAAC.

28:23.970 --> 28:26.598
Isaac: ABBY? [ LAUGHS ]

28:26.630 --> 28:28.962
ABBY?

28:34.710 --> 28:36.337
Abigail: ISAAC.

28:36.380 --> 28:37.608
Isaac: HOW DID YOU --

28:37.640 --> 28:40.746
Abigail: Shh. MY SWEET.

28:40.780 --> 28:42.941
TELL ME --

28:42.980 --> 28:46.086
WHO WAS WITH YOU IN THE WOODS?

28:46.120 --> 28:49.009
Isaac: WHO WAS WHAT?

28:49.060 --> 28:52.723
Abigail: THE OTHER NIGHT.
WHO WAS WITH YOU?

28:59.830 --> 29:03.630
Mary: WHO WAS WITH YOU,
MY SWEET ISAAC?

29:06.840 --> 29:08.705
Abigail:
WHO WAS WITH YOU, MY LOVE?

29:08.740 --> 29:11.277
NO ONE CAN HEAR US.

29:15.350 --> 29:19.138
IF YOU LOVE ME, YOU'LL TELL ME.

29:25.690 --> 29:27.089
Isaac: I CAN'T.

29:27.130 --> 29:29.155
Abigail: TELL ME,
AND WE'LL BE TOGETHER AGAIN,

29:29.200 --> 29:32.124
JUST LIKE WE WERE.

29:32.170 --> 29:33.728
Isaac: [ SIGHS ]

29:33.770 --> 29:35.169
I CAN'T.

29:35.200 --> 29:36.963
Abigail: YOU CAN.

29:37.000 --> 29:38.661
Isaac: I CAN'T.

29:38.710 --> 29:40.302
Cotton: YOU CAN'T WHAT?

29:40.340 --> 29:44.106
Abigail: YOU CAN. IT'S OKAY.

29:44.150 --> 29:46.539
WHO WAS WITH YOU, MY LOVE?

29:49.550 --> 29:51.780
Isaac: IT WAS JOHN ALDEN.

30:00.490 --> 30:01.957
[ DOOR OPENS ]

30:02.000 --> 30:04.491
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

30:04.530 --> 30:07.021
Mary:
GOOD MORNING, MAGISTRATE.

30:07.070 --> 30:08.992
Mr. Hale:
GOOD MORNING, MRS. SIBLEY.

30:09.040 --> 30:10.337
WHAT AN UNFORESEEN DELIGHT.

30:10.370 --> 30:12.702
WILL YOU JOIN ME IN SOME COFFEE?

30:12.740 --> 30:15.607
W-WE'VE BEEN EXPERIMENTING
WITH A NEW BRAZILIAN BREW.

30:15.640 --> 30:16.868
Mary: MAY WE SPEAK?

30:21.380 --> 30:23.814
Mr. Hale:
THE LADIES ARE AT PRAYER.

30:23.850 --> 30:27.240
Mary: HE WAS ALONE -- ISAAC.

30:28.420 --> 30:30.718
Mr. Hale:
YOU QUESTIONED HIM? HOW?

30:30.760 --> 30:32.887
Mary:
HE WAS ALONE IN THE WOODS.

30:32.930 --> 30:34.352
AND THAT ENDS THIS PERSECUTION.

30:34.400 --> 30:35.628
Mr. Hale:
AND YOU'RE ABSOLUTELY CERTAIN

30:35.660 --> 30:37.355
THAT ISAAC WAS TELLING
THE TRUTH?

30:37.400 --> 30:39.197
Mary: THE CIRCUMSTANCES WERE
SUCH THAT A LIE WOULD NOT --

30:39.230 --> 30:41.960
COULD NOT -- CROSS HIS LIPS.

30:42.000 --> 30:44.230
Mr. Hale:
WELL, THEN, THAT LEAVES NOTHING

30:44.270 --> 30:46.329
BUT TO TASK THE SELECTMEN
TO A VOTE

30:46.370 --> 30:48.179
AND HANG THE BOY FOR WITCHCRAFT.

30:48.210 --> 30:49.837
Mary: NO.

30:49.880 --> 30:51.370
Mr. Hale: SALEM WILL BE
NO POORER FOR ONE LESS NITWIT.

30:52.710 --> 30:54.246
Mary: NO.

30:54.280 --> 30:56.748
Mr. Hale: [ SIGHS ]

30:56.780 --> 30:59.419
WE WILL NEVER TRULY KNOW
WHAT HE SAW,

30:59.450 --> 31:01.680
AND WHAT HE SAW
COULD GET US ALL KILLED.

31:01.720 --> 31:04.757
Mary: I CAN CONTROL ISAAC.

31:04.790 --> 31:06.348
Mr. Hale:
AND WHAT OF THE GRAND RITE?

31:06.390 --> 31:08.722
YOU WANTED ANOTHER VICTIM,
AND NOW YOU HAVE ONE.

31:08.760 --> 31:11.661
TICK-TOCK, MRS. SIBLEY.
THE NEXT MOON FAST APPROACHES.

31:11.700 --> 31:13.122
Mary:
I WILL NOT LET THIS HAPPEN.

31:14.240 --> 31:15.696
Mr. Hale:
YOU'RE POWERLESS TO STOP IT.

31:15.740 --> 31:17.765
THE COUNCIL WILL RULE
OVERWHELMINGLY AGAINST IT.

31:17.800 --> 31:19.199
Mary: YOU WILL NOT DO THIS!
[ PLATE RATTLES ]

31:22.610 --> 31:25.170
Mr. Hale: IT CAN ONLY BE
SENTIMENT THAT'S STOPPING YOU.

31:25.210 --> 31:27.576
SUCH RAW EMOTION.

31:27.610 --> 31:29.919
IT MAKES YOU VULNERABLE.

31:29.950 --> 31:31.611
DON'T LET IT CLOUD YOUR PURPOSE.

31:31.650 --> 31:33.049
HE HAS TO GO.

31:34.620 --> 31:37.282
Anne: MRS. SIBLEY.

31:37.320 --> 31:39.550
Mary: GOOD MORNING, ANNE.

31:43.900 --> 31:45.094
Isaac: THEY AIN'T MINE.

31:45.130 --> 31:48.463
I'VE SAID IT
10 WAYS FROM SUNDAY!

31:48.500 --> 31:50.388
Cotton: THEN HOW DID THEY COME
TO BE ON YOUR PERSON?

31:50.440 --> 31:52.465
Isaac: I DON'T KNOW. THE PIGMAN
MUST HAVE PUT THEM ON ME.

31:52.510 --> 31:54.876
OR THAT BLASTED SPECT ER
FROM THE CRAGS.

31:54.910 --> 31:56.309
Cotton: THE PIGMAN?

31:56.340 --> 31:59.138
Isaac: HE SAW US THAT NIGHT
IN THE WOODS.

31:59.180 --> 32:01.648
THAT'S WHY THEY'RE DOING THIS
TO ME.

32:01.680 --> 32:04.410
DON'T YOU SEE?
THEY KNOW I SEEN SOMETHING.

32:04.450 --> 32:07.681
[ HORSE NEIGHS ]

32:09.090 --> 32:10.284
[ SIGHS ]

32:10.320 --> 32:11.628
Cotton:
WHAT ELSE DO YOU REMEMBER?

32:14.830 --> 32:16.354
-Isaac: FROM THE WOODS?
-Cotton: NO.

32:18.970 --> 32:20.198
FROM THE OTHER NIGHT.

32:23.600 --> 32:27.309
AT -- AT THE ROD?

32:28.340 --> 32:30.877
Isaac: THE WHOREHOUSE?

32:35.280 --> 32:37.840
NOTHING.
I-I-I DON'T REMEMBER ANYTHING.

32:37.880 --> 32:39.142
I TOLD YOU...

32:40.490 --> 32:42.788
Mary: CAPTAIN, A WORD.

32:51.030 --> 32:53.362
MAGISTRATE HALE
WILL BE HERE SOON FOR ISAAC.

32:53.400 --> 32:55.994
HE'S PREPARED TO FORCE A VOTE
AND HANG HIM.

32:56.040 --> 32:58.508
YOU WILL STOP HIM.

32:58.540 --> 33:00.269
John: HOW?

33:00.310 --> 33:02.972
Mary: ANY WAY YOU MUST.

33:10.680 --> 33:14.355
Mr. Hale: WELL, THE BUSINESS
OF SALEM AWAITS NO MAN.

33:14.390 --> 33:16.984
Anne: I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE DOING,
AND I HATE YOU FOR IT.

33:17.020 --> 33:19.682
Mrs. Hale:
UNACCEPTABLE LANGUAGE.

33:19.730 --> 33:23.848
UTTERLY AND COMPLETELY HORRID
SENTIMENT.

33:23.900 --> 33:27.859
Anne: MY FRIEND IS DEAD.

33:29.200 --> 33:31.839
AND YOU RUSH OUT
TO KILL ANOTHER.

33:31.870 --> 33:33.565
Mr. Hale: DARLING,
YOU MUST UNDERSTAND --

33:33.610 --> 33:35.009
Anne: EVEN MARY SIBLEY,

33:35.040 --> 33:37.975
WITH WHOM I SHARE
NOT A SINGLE COMMON OPINION,

33:38.010 --> 33:39.705
FINDS YOUR ACTIONS VILE!

33:39.750 --> 33:41.741
Mr. Hale: AND JUST HOW MUCH
OF MY CONVERSATION

33:41.780 --> 33:43.748
DID YOU FEEL YOURSELF
ENTITLED TO?

33:43.780 --> 33:46.248
Anne: ENOUGH TO KNOW THAT THIS
PERSECUTION OF ISAAC IS FOLLY!

33:46.290 --> 33:49.418
WILL YOU KILL ANOTHER, FATHER?

33:49.460 --> 33:51.928
IS THAT THE "BUSINESS"
YOU'RE SO EAGER TO ATTEND TO?

33:51.960 --> 33:55.418
Mr. Hale: EVERYTHING I DO,
I DO FOR THIS FAMILY...

33:55.460 --> 33:58.224
FOR ITS WELL-BEING

33:58.270 --> 34:00.420
AND FOR THE GREATER GOOD
OF THIS TOWN.

34:05.970 --> 34:07.267
[ DOOR OPENS ]

34:09.740 --> 34:11.844
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

34:11.880 --> 34:13.575
Anne: WHAT?

34:13.610 --> 34:17.944
NO "HOW DARE YOU?"
"MIND YOUR ELDERS"?

34:17.980 --> 34:20.289
Mrs. Hale: FOR ONCE,
MY DAUGHTER, I AGREE WITH YOU.

34:26.560 --> 34:28.050
Anne: YOU DO?

34:28.100 --> 34:31.524
Mrs. Hale: BUT IF I WERE YOU,
I'D FIND AN AVENUE

34:31.570 --> 34:33.959
AROUND YOUR DISTASTE
FOR MRS. SIBLEY

34:34.000 --> 34:37.788
IN ORDER TO ABSORB
HER MANNERS AND WAYS.

34:37.840 --> 34:39.967
Anne: SHE'S DESPICABLE.
I COULD NEVER BE LIKE HER.

34:40.010 --> 34:42.979
Mrs. Hale: SHE IS A WOMAN WHO
HAS FOUND HER WAY TO A VOICE.

34:43.010 --> 34:44.477
Anne: LOOK HOW SHE USES IT.

34:44.510 --> 34:46.239
Mrs. Hale: YOU COULD USE YOURS
ANY WAY YOU LIKE,

34:46.280 --> 34:49.716
BUT YOU HAVE TO FIND IT FIRST,

34:49.750 --> 34:51.786
UNLESS YOU WANT TO SPEND
THE REST OF YOUR LIFE

34:51.820 --> 34:54.288
SHOUTING AT YOUR FATHER...

34:54.320 --> 34:58.017
OR...YOUR HUSBAND.

35:05.100 --> 35:07.591
Cotton:
WHAT DID MRS. SIBLEY REQUIRE?

35:07.630 --> 35:10.292
John: ARE YOU CONVINCED
OF ISAAC'S INNOCENCE OR GUILT?

35:10.340 --> 35:14.003
Cotton: I AM NOT CONVINCED
OF EITHER.

35:14.040 --> 35:16.679
John: THEN STAY THE HELL
OUT OF MY WAY.

35:16.710 --> 35:19.406
Mr. Hale:
WE SHALL TAKE THE BOY TO TRIAL.

35:19.450 --> 35:20.678
John:
THAT PATH LEADS TO THE GALLOWS.

35:20.710 --> 35:23.178
Mr. Hale:
IT'S IN NO ONE MAN'S HANDS.

35:23.220 --> 35:25.484
John:
REALLY? WHOSE HANDS IS IT IN?

35:25.520 --> 35:29.081
Mr. Hale: GOD'S, OF COURSE.

35:29.120 --> 35:31.008
John: NO.

35:31.060 --> 35:34.029
Mr. Hale:
NEED I REMIND YOU, SON,

35:34.060 --> 35:36.324
THAT YOU ARE IMPEDING
THE VERY SAME MAN

35:36.360 --> 35:38.863
WHO ONLY YESTERDAY
WAS YOUR SAVIOR?

35:38.900 --> 35:40.595
John: YEAH.
THAT WAS YESTERDAY.

35:40.630 --> 35:42.530
YOU WANT ISAAC TODAY...

35:42.570 --> 35:44.731
YOU GOT TO GO THROUGH ME.

35:47.840 --> 35:52.174
Mr. Hale: THE GREAT JOHN ALDEN
DISAPPEARS FOR A DECADE

35:52.210 --> 35:57.045
AND THEN DARES TO COME BACK
AND DICTATE HOW TO RUN OUR TOWN?

35:57.080 --> 35:58.741
TAKE HIM.

36:07.590 --> 36:09.399
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

36:10.700 --> 36:12.895
Tituba:
HE IS NOT WORTH THIS ISAAC.

36:12.930 --> 36:14.966
Mary: THIS HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH ISAAC.

36:15.000 --> 36:18.037
Tituba: I KNOW. WHICH MEANS
IT HAS TO DO WITH JOHN ALDEN.

36:18.070 --> 36:20.959
Mary: THE MAGISTRATE
WILL LEARN WHO LEADS US,

36:21.010 --> 36:22.705
AND HE WILL ACCEPT IT.

36:22.740 --> 36:23.832
Titu ba: OR?

36:28.250 --> 36:29.547
[ SNAKE HISSES ]

37:20.000 --> 37:21.399
[ GASPS ]

37:27.670 --> 37:29.604
[ GASPING ]

37:33.180 --> 37:34.716
[ CHOKING ]

37:47.130 --> 37:49.997
John: [ GRUNTING ]

37:57.540 --> 38:00.134
Cotton: HELP HIM.

38:00.170 --> 38:01.979
Isaac: [ SCREAMS ]

38:02.010 --> 38:03.637
Messenger: MAGISTRATE HALE,
YOUR DAUGHTER!

38:03.680 --> 38:06.604
Mr. Hale: STOP!
GET HIM BACK IN THE CELL!

38:06.650 --> 38:09.141
STOP! STOP!

38:10.480 --> 38:11.788
GET HIM BACK IN THE CELL!

38:11.820 --> 38:13.515
WHAT? WHAT'S HAPPENED?

38:13.550 --> 38:15.609
Isaac: [ GRUNTING ]

38:16.990 --> 38:18.685
Lamb:
HAS SHE ET SOMETHING STRANGE

38:18.730 --> 38:20.254
-FROM THE GARDEN OR THE WOODS?
-Mrs. Hale: NO.

38:20.290 --> 38:22.497
Lamb: WAS SHE BIT
BY AN INSECT OR A CRITTER?

38:22.530 --> 38:24.623
-MrS. Hale: NO, NO! PLEASE!
-Mr. Hale: WHAT'S HAPPENED?

38:24.670 --> 38:26.991
Mrs. Hale:
SHE -- SHE CAN'T BREATHE!

38:27.030 --> 38:28.964
Mr. Hale: FOR GOD'S SAKES, MAN,
DO SOMETHING!

38:29.000 --> 38:31.139
Lamb:
SHE IS BEYOND MY ARTS.

38:31.170 --> 38:32.899
Anne: [ CHOKING ]

38:39.880 --> 38:41.575
Mrs. Hale: WHERE --

38:44.590 --> 38:45.818
[ DOOR OPENS ]

38:45.850 --> 38:49.308
Mr. Hale:
STOP IT! MAKE IT STOP!

38:49.360 --> 38:51.180
Mary:
MAGISTRATE, GOOD AFTERNOON.

38:51.220 --> 38:52.824
Mr. Hale: I BEG OF YOU. ISAAC
CAN GO FREE, WHATEVER YOU WANT.

38:52.860 --> 38:54.054
JUST MAKE IT STOP.

38:54.090 --> 38:55.398
Mary:
YOU WILL NOT QUESTION HIM.

38:55.430 --> 38:56.692
Mr. Hale: NO.

38:56.730 --> 38:58.322
Mary:
YOU WILL GET OUT OF MY WAY.

38:58.370 --> 39:00.497
YOU WILL LET ME LEAD
WITHOUT FURTHER INTERFERENCE.

39:00.530 --> 39:02.794
I WILL CHOOSE
WHO LIVES AND WHO DIES.

39:02.840 --> 39:04.831
Mr. Hale: YES, YES.
HELP HER.

39:07.340 --> 39:09.672
Mary: YOU SEE, MAGISTRATE,

39:09.710 --> 39:13.202
I'VE LOST EVERYTHING IN
THIS TOWN THAT I EVER CARED FOR.

39:13.250 --> 39:15.013
YOU, HOWEVER,

39:15.050 --> 39:17.041
YOU HAVE EVERYTHING LEFT
TO LOSE --

39:17.080 --> 39:20.846
A SENTIMENT
THAT MAKES YOU VULNERABLE.

39:20.890 --> 39:22.585
Mr. Hale: [ SIGHS ]

39:22.620 --> 39:26.886
PLEASE. MY DAUGHTER.

39:28.530 --> 39:32.022
MY DAUGHTER.

39:35.140 --> 39:37.199
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

39:43.740 --> 39:47.574
Mrs. Hale: SHE'S IMPROVED.

39:47.610 --> 39:49.749
Mr. Hale: [ SIGHS ]

39:51.250 --> 39:54.959
I NEVER UNDERSTOOD IT BEFORE --

39:54.990 --> 39:58.255
HOW MY PARENTS
COULD SEND ME AWAY.

39:58.290 --> 40:00.520
WHAT COULD BE WORSE
THAN BEING APART?

40:00.560 --> 40:03.893
CERTAINLY NOT DEATH.

40:05.800 --> 40:09.031
NOW I KNOW A PARENT
WILL DO ANYTHING

40:09.070 --> 40:11.766
FOR THE LIFE OF THEIR CHILD.

40:15.840 --> 40:17.569
Mrs. Hale: WHAT DID YOU DO?

40:20.080 --> 40:21.479
Anne: WHAT HAPPENED?

40:21.520 --> 40:23.545
Mr. Hale:
IT'S ALL RIGHT, DARLING.

40:23.580 --> 40:25.844
EVERYTHING'S GOING TO BE
ALL RIGHT.

40:30.820 --> 40:32.526
[ SMOOCHES ]

40:33.760 --> 40:35.318
John: [ GROANS ]

40:35.360 --> 40:38.488
Cotton: A CONFESSION --

40:38.530 --> 40:40.498
I'VE THOUGHT, ON OCCASION, MY
CHARACTER MIGHT'VE BEEN IMPROVED

40:40.530 --> 40:42.930
BY THE INFREQUENT TUSSLE.

40:44.810 --> 40:46.266
John: OH, YEAH.

40:46.310 --> 40:48.005
BEATING'S DONE YOU
A WORLD OF GOOD.

40:52.480 --> 40:53.947
WHY DID YOU HELP ME?

40:55.150 --> 40:57.573
Cotton:
EVEN GOD DEMANDS A FAIR FIGHT.

40:57.620 --> 40:59.918
Mr. Hale: GENTLEMEN.

40:59.950 --> 41:02.418
THE SELECTMEN AND I FEEL,
IN THIS PARTICULAR CASE,

41:02.460 --> 41:04.758
THAT A TRIAL AND A VOTE
WILL BE UNNECESSARY.

41:04.790 --> 41:07.782
CLEARLY, THE LAD WAS DRUNK.

41:07.830 --> 41:10.458
WE ARE WILLING TO LET HIM GO
AND DROP CHARGES.

41:13.030 --> 41:15.464
UNLESS, OF COURSE,
THE REVEREND FEELS OTHERWISE.

41:16.670 --> 41:18.763
Cotton:
A DRUNKEN ROMP IS ALL --

41:18.810 --> 41:21.904
A YOUNG MAN'S PREROGATIVE.

41:31.820 --> 41:33.515
WHY DON'T YOU TELL HIM?

41:49.870 --> 41:52.168
John: WELL...

41:52.210 --> 41:54.531
THE GOOD FOLKS OF SALEM

41:54.580 --> 41:58.004
HAVE DECLARED YOU A DRUNK
AND NOT A WITCH.

41:58.040 --> 42:00.201
YOU'RE SPRUNG.

42:02.780 --> 42:04.213
Isaac: I'M FREE?

42:04.250 --> 42:07.515
John: YEAH.
GET THE HELL OUT OF HERE.

42:07.550 --> 42:11.680
Isaac: PRETTY SURE NO ONE'S
EVER STOOD FOR ME BEFORE.

42:11.730 --> 42:13.880
MAKES IT HARD TO KNOW
WHAT TO SAY.

42:19.200 --> 42:21.862
YOU SAVED MY LIFE.

42:39.950 --> 42:41.884
Cotton: EXCELLENT NEWS.

42:41.920 --> 42:44.855
ISAAC HAS BEEN SPARED.

42:44.890 --> 42:46.755
Gloriana: WHAT? HOW?

42:46.790 --> 42:50.089
Cotton: THERE SIMPLY WASN'T THE
REQUIRED EVIDENCE TO CONVICT.

42:50.130 --> 42:52.189
I TOLD YOU I WAS THOROUGH

42:52.230 --> 42:53.868
AND THAT THE INNOCENT...

42:53.900 --> 42:56.562
HAVE NO CAUSE FOR ALARM.

42:59.170 --> 43:01.968
DOES THAT NOT GIVE YOU PEACE?

43:02.010 --> 43:03.773
Gloriana: THAT IS TODAY,

43:03.810 --> 43:05.903
BUT WHAT OF THE DAYS
THAT FOLLOW?

43:05.950 --> 43:09.249
Cotton:
WE WILL TAKE THEM AS THEY COME.

43:09.280 --> 43:10.747
Gloriana: WE WILL?

43:10.780 --> 43:13.089
Cotton: I TOLD YOU --
NO HARM WILL COME TO YOU.

43:13.120 --> 43:14.382
Gloriana: YOU CAN'T BE SURE.

43:14.420 --> 43:17.116
Cotton: I CAN.

43:22.530 --> 43:24.418
Gloriana:
DO YOU EVER WONDER?

43:24.460 --> 43:26.667
Cotton: WHAT?

43:28.870 --> 43:31.259
Gloriana:
IF WE COULD LEAVE THIS PLACE?

43:32.770 --> 43:35.807
IF WE COULD FORGET SALEM
AND ITS WITCHES?

43:37.510 --> 43:40.104
IF WE COULD HAVE
A DIFFERENT LIFE?

43:42.820 --> 43:45.641
Cotton:
I BELIEVE I'M DOING GOOD.

43:45.690 --> 43:47.783
Gloriana: I KNOW.

43:50.790 --> 43:54.453
AND YOUR FATHER
WOULD BE SO VERY PROUD.

44:47.710 --> 44:49.871
[ BELL TOLLING ]

44:52.690 --> 44:55.056
Mary: ISAAC HAS BEEN FREED?

44:55.090 --> 44:56.717
John: YES.

44:58.060 --> 45:00.187
Mary: GOOD.

45:05.100 --> 45:07.523
John:
YOU SHOULD SEE THE MILITIA.

45:13.270 --> 45:14.567
Mary: I'M GRATEFUL.

45:16.310 --> 45:17.902
FOR ISAAC.

45:22.250 --> 45:24.241
John: OKAY, THEN.

45:25.490 --> 45:28.687
Mary: JOHN...

45:28.720 --> 45:31.211
WE WERE FORTUNATE TODAY,

45:31.260 --> 45:33.888
BUT WE MIGHT NOT BE SO LUCKY
IN DAYS TO COME.

45:33.930 --> 45:35.989
IF YOU INSIST ON STAYING...

45:38.100 --> 45:41.991
...YOU MUST UNDERSTAND
I CANNOT PROTECT YOU.

46:34.320 --> 46:36.652
George: [ GARGLES ]

46:54.240 --> 46:57.300
-- Captions by VITAC --
